{"tid":400626,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【關公災難】網民質疑Pokeguide抽錯水 港鐵早與其他App合作","createTime":"2017-09-15T03:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T04:34:02.000Z","uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83108dbd4aca4a77da2f1515974cd6507fa9fca4","tid":400626,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170915&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=57212564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170915%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D57212564&d=LudQIL6f%2B2Q6d8%2BvPPualZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=0f512793\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170915%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D57212564&h=1a9f67c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170915&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=57212564</a>"},{"pid":"a01bf8fcfbd6bafc2e3d0d02fe3fbef33cc7790a","tid":400626,"uid":78546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:11:58.000Z","msg":"昨日凌晨在facebook pages大控訴，質疑港鐵（006）疑似抄襲「車站內搜索功能」以及「快捷出站」功能其idea的Pokeguide，今日凌晨再度fb出post，指港鐵未有回應其中一個idea，在地鐵站內加beacon引導乘客出站入站，質疑港鐵不向Pokeguide或其他App尋求合作，而是自資過千萬再做車站資料。不過本報及有網民發現，其實港鐵早在8月31日公佈，和其中一個App Citymapper合作，令人質疑Pokeguide控訴港鐵抄襲idea的說法。<br />\n<br />\nPokeguide今日凌晨新post表示，其要求港鐵回應兩點，包括兩個idea，一是「地鐵站內加beacon可以引導人入站出站」，二為「 地鐵幕門加beacon除咗幫助傷健人仕，仲可以偵測有幾多人出入車廂，從而建議大家可以走去比較空嘅車廂等車。」<br />\n<br />\nPokeguide表示跟港鐵高層開會後，港鐵就上亦第二點作回應指，已使用另一種技術偵測車廂人流狀況。但第一點卻以「呢個idea好好，我哋會返去研究吓。」Pokeguide就第一點，質疑港鐵寧願花過千萬自資推出功能，亦不尋他們或其他已有資料的startup合作。並呼籲網民除了下載Pokeguide，亦可以下載「速逃」、「MTRush」以及「Citymapper」等擁有類似功能的App，方便搭港鐵。<br />\n<br />\n但事實上，港鐵在8月31日的公佈，為提升Traffic News 功能，在出現較長時間的車務延誤時，適時為乘客提供車務資訊及其他交通工具的資料，會在網頁及Traffic News加入前往Citymapper的連結，在車務事故期間，乘客可按其需要獲取更全面的公共交通工具資料。<br />\n<br />\n即是港鐵就加強乘客取得乘車資訊方面，已跟Citymapper合作，但目前仍未跟Pokeguide合作。<br />\n<br />\n有網民質疑Pokeguide，認為港鐵已官方宣佈跟「Citymapper合作」，亦有網民表示，「人地新聞稿話揀同citymapper合作點解你地隻字不提？地鐵揀左對家公司就發爛咋？」，亦有網民支持Pokeguide，認為港鐵過橋抽板。"},{"pid":"68616d59b31c3615087e69fbf7a80a4fe78da486","tid":400626,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c8812a8c1e9f1871dd069dbec237ce31f2bb89","tid":400626,"uid":57705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:45:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41fcb4bcaf10f64615e10e040812d45513e3bba7","tid":400626,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"港鐵（006）???"},{"pid":"744192327502ff752213c88541fdcf4de2446e14","tid":400626,"uid":40925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地自己data做乜撚一定要同你合作<br />\n人地肯駛千幾萬，關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />on99</blockquote><br />\n咪就係 on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f52e96eadb15f12f4a45571a3eab3bd5db02d2","tid":400626,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地自己data做乜撚一定要同你合作<br />\n人地肯駛千幾萬，關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />on99</blockquote><br />\n咪就係 on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔幫襯你 幫襯左人地 就發爛渣<br />\n好酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17afb493e158bd644cf00d9a4